Class SWTCheckBox

java.lang.Object
  dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.form.SWTCheckBox
All Implemented Interfaces:
dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.form.internal.ISWTWidgetElement, ISWTWidget
public class SWTCheckBox
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISWTWidget, dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.form.internal.ISWTWidgetElement

This standard widget represents a checkbox. The widget does not include a label. A checkbox can be created with the following code snippet: 

 WidgetFactory factory = getWidgetFactory();
 factory.createLabel( parent, "CheckBoxWidgetId", "CheckBoxMementoId", "CheckBox Label" );
 
 factory.createCheckBox( parent, "CheckBoxWidgetId", "CheckBoxMementoId" );
